scovery journey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.slideshare.net/joshzhu/nginx-internals\">Nginx Internals</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.nginx.com/blog/inside-nginx-how-we-designed-for-performance-scale/\">Inside NGINX: How We Designed for Performance &#x26; Scale</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.nginx.com/blog/thread-pools-boost-performance-9x/\">Thread Pools in NGINX</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"configuration\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#configuration\" aria-label=\"configuration permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Configuration</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://nginx.org/en/docs/beginners_guide.html\">Beginner's Guide</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nginx.org/en/docs/varindex.html\">Alphabetical index of variables</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.nginx.com/resources/wiki/start/topics/tutorials/config_pitfalls/\">Nginx Pitfalls</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.engineyard.com/useful-rewrites-for-nginx\">Useful Rewrites for Nginx</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.martinfjordvald.com/nginx-primer/\">Nginx Configuration Primer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.martinfjordvald.com/nginx-primer-2-from-apache-to-nginx/\">Nginx Primer 2: From Apache to Nginx</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.martinfjordvald.com/understanding-the-nginx-configuration-inheritance-model/\">Understanding the Nginx Configuration Inheritance Model</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/h5bp/server-configs-nginx\">Nginx HTTP server boilerplate configs</a><a data-role=\"